description:
As you might have guessed looking at the length of the video, this isn't the super long project I've been working on. This is something small I put together in the last week after I found this Tim Pool video and it annoyed me.

Lately I haven't had too much time to work on videos, so hopefully a simple video like this one will help bridge the content gap while I finish my next big project.

And if Tim Pool is reading this, please link sources in your videos. You only had one article. It isn't that hard.

If you liked this video, you can follow me on Twitter here: https://twitter.com/JoseNotAJay

If you have any burning questions for me, you can ask them here: https://curiouscat.me/JoseNotAJay

My Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/JoseOnYoutube

Sources
Tim Pool video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EzIaxQb2nzQ&t=66s

Vox article
https://www.vox.com/the-goods/2018/10/24/18014276/mens-rights-activist-eagle-rock-brewery-lawsuit

https://losangeles.cbslocal.com/2014/11/05/jury-sides-with-brea-restaurant-in-senorita-night-discrimination-lawsuit/
http://www.latimes.com/politics/la-na-pol-trump-mens-rights-20161027-story.html
